{
  "stem": "18474.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a lot of religious Jews there, they were-- had beards and they didn't want to be shaved.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they-- so they used to take a scarf and tie it around their beard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they-- they-- they had to shave their beards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they took a barber and they took a big rock in that place where they blew up that palace.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a big rock there and-- and they picked out the Jews with the beards and bring it to him and he had to shave them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As the tractor drove by and he was standing against the rock, he turned the tractor with his chains against that rock.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He chopped both his feet off, the barber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He started to holler.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the German, the one who was driving the tractor, took out a gun, shot him right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- so we knew we were in trouble, very much so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the airport, there were different people working there and there were telephone lines and whatever running on the airport.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They took and they-- some kind of line got cut.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the nearest 12 guys that were working to fill in the holes there, they took them out and they shot them, from my home town.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But actually, they didn't cut the line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A tractor ran by and cut the line.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they blamed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So life didn't mean nothing no more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew-- we knew-- this is-- incidents-- every day, something else happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My daily life, go to work and we-- then my father went somewhere else to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sisters--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There-- lots of times, I used to go, I knew farmers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they needed help, I used to go and work for nothing just to keep me away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
